{{title 'Combats'}}
<h1>Combats</h1>

<p>The combat directory lists active combats and allows you to view combat status in a web page rather than typing 'combat' over and over in your MUSH window.  Organizers can also perform some setup activities via the web.</p>

<table class="table table-striped">
<thead>
    <th>Combat ID</th>
    <th>Organizer</th>
    <th>Participants</th>
</thead>

<tbody>
{{#each model as |combat|}}
<tr><td>
    {{#link-to 'combat' combat.id}}{{combat.id}}{{/link-to}}
</td>

<td>
    {{combat.organizer}}
</td>

<td>
    {{#each combat.participants as |p|}}
    {{p}}
    {{/each}}
</td>

</tr>
{{/each}}
</tbody>
</table>


{{outlet}}